		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凶面放开枉死之面，面具追踪玩家，随后闭合爆炸，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
