			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凶面将枉死之面拼合，随后推行，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="426" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当玩家距离凶面&gt;7m时，其就会开始格挡攻击。</p>
